headline.main: Peak Gasoline Demand Looms With Engine Efficiency Gains
headline.print_headline: Peak Gasoline Demand Looms With Engine Efficiency Gains

lead_paragraph: Irish nationalists Sinn Fein and the pro-British Democratic Unionist Party were neck-and-neck on Friday almost halfway through the counting of votes in a snap election that could dramatically shift the balance of power in Northern Ireland.
